  <brief_title>Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy for Acute Calculous Cholecystitis in the Elderly: A Retrospective Study.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy for Acute Calculous Cholecystitis in the Elderly: More Complex But Equally Safe and Effective. A Retrospective Study on 879 Patients.</official_title>
